    <node id="Abrupt Cut">
      <data key="d0">Abrupt Cut</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Abrupt Cut is a technique used in visual storytelling that abruptly changes the scene or perspective, capturing viewer attention.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d3e75cfe6e58b04c27e92833c1cbcd28</data>
