    </node>
    <node id="Listicle Content">
      <data key="d0">Listicle Content</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">Listicle Content is a format that presents information in a list format, often used to capture interest through intriguing titles.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-860b31095f79179d4d612439410f152e</data>
      <data key="d4">knowledge:viral-hooks:curiosity-gap</data>
      <data key="d5">1778002939</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Behind-the-Scenes Videos">
      <data key="d0">Behind-the-Scenes Videos</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">Behind-the-Scenes Videos are types of content that reveal the process or secrets behind certain topics, enhancing viewer engagement.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-860b31095f79179d4d612439410f152e</data>
      <data key="d4">knowledge:viral-hooks:curiosity-gap</data>
      <data key="d5">1778002939</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Tutorial Content">
      <data key="d0">Tutorial Content</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">Tutorial Content provides instructional or educational material aimed at teaching viewers specific skills or concepts.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-860b31095f79179d4d612439410f152e</data>
      <data key="d4">knowledge:viral-hooks:curiosity-gap</data>
      <data key="d5">1778002939</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Zeigarnik Effect">
      <data key="d0">Zeigarnik Effect</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The Zeigarnik Effect is a psychological phenomenon where incomplete tasks create a cognitive urge for resolution, leading to increased focus on those tasks.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-860b31095f79179d4d612439410f152e</data>
      <data key="d4">knowledge:viral-hooks:curiosity-gap</data>
      <data key="d5">1778002939</data>
