      <data key="d0">Marketing Tactic</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Marketing Tactic refers to specific strategies used to improve business performance, with one highlighted as being particularly effective.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-860b31095f79179d4d612439410f152e</data>
