      <data key="d0">7-Figure Business</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">A 7-Figure Business refers to a business that generates annual revenue in the seven-digit range, often signifying a successful entrepreneurial venture.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-860b31095f79179d4d612439410f152e</data>
