      <data key="d2">Social Media Platforms include Instagram, Facebook, and LinkedIn, where multi-slide posts can be effectively utilized.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-15d3c57e1c04f91cc88c3fede244761c</data>
      <data key="d4">knowledge:visual-design:carousel-pacing</data>
